{
  "stem": "22174.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And he had given it to a farmer, to workers, you know, to a peasant.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were a group of about, I would say, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] maybe 10 or 12 young people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, girls and guys, all Jewish, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All German except one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No, two.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One was from Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the other one, yeah, came also from Germany, but he was from Eastern Europe, immigrated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, and it was a very nice group of young people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we all worked as this peasant taught us how to work, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We all came from a militarized bourgeois environment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know how to work with tools, and farming, agriculture, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I only had learned it in the forest, so I was [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] more [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] success.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was already the expert, so to say.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you know, so it was a beautiful town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of the happiest times I ever had in my life in Italy, there in northern Italy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father thought that when he made this agreement with the forester that I would learn forestry, because, at that time, and also in later years, forests were planted very much in Palestine, and then later in Israel.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even today, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because to improve the climate, and the soil.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so my father thought forestry would be a good profession there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But forestry in Germany and planting trees in Israel are quite a different story.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, there was no expertise in anything like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was very different forestry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, there was no lumbering there.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
